    h1 Neo4j for Ruby

  #content.col-xs-9
    .panel
      .panel-heading
        h3 What is Neo4j.rb?
      .panel-body
        p Neo4j.rb (neo4j gem) is a Ruby wrapper for the Neo4j graph database.  It is a “Drop in” replacement for Rails Active Record.
        p Top Features
        ul
          li
            | Object Model interface for Nodes and Relationships including:
            ul
              li Properties
              li Indexes / Constraints
              li Callbacks
              li Validation
              li Assocations
          li
            | Query building / chaining interface similar to
            = link_to "arel", "https://github.com/rails/arel"
          li Transactions
          li Migrations

